                                proceedings take <strong>6 to 18 months</strong>. After the court decree, a mandatory
                                <strong>90-day Iddat period</strong> follows before the NADRA Divorce Effectiveness
                                Certificate is issued, making the total process 6 to 21 months end-to-end.</p>
                            <p class="faq-related">Learn more: <a href="/services/khula-procedure/">Khula Procedure Services</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-box reveal">
                        <h3 class="faq-box-question">Can my husband stop me from getting Khula?</h3>
                        <div class="faq-box-answer">
